<% layout('layouts/boilerplate')%>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <h1 class="text-center mt-5">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <hr>
    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2>1. What payment methods can I use to make a donation?</h2>
        <p>We accept donations through Mercado Pago, which accepts various forms of payment such as credit and debit cards.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2>2. How do I create an account?</h2>
        <p>To create an account, click on the "Sign Up" button and fill out the registration form. Please note that your account will not be active until you verify your email address. A verification link will be sent to the email address you provided during registration.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2>3. Why do I need to verify my email address?</h2>
        <p>Email verification is a security measure to ensure that the email address provided belongs to the user. This also helps us communicate updates from the donation places you've supported.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2>4. How will I know about the updates from the places I've donated to?</h2>
        <p>The places you've donated to will send an annual update to your registered email address, sharing their progress and how your donations have contributed to their cause.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2>5. What currency are the donations in?</h2>
        <p>All donations are processed in Argentine Pesos (ARS).</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2>6. What if I have more questions?</h2>
        <p>If you have any further questions, please feel free to contact our customer service. We'll be more than happy to assist you.</p>
    </section>
</div>

